<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Recovery from sickness. ƲIT156</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba A̱ki a̱ kana ma!
 Is sa̱ nukha̱klo tuk oka
 Chi anukfihinli li kʋt,
 Na̱ yukpʋt chin taloa li.

[V2]
 Si abeka fehna tuk ash
 Is sa hlakoffichi kʋno;
 Sa nipi kia hotupa ma,
 Ish nuktalali hokʋno.

[V3]
 Sʋlla hinla tuk pulla kia,
 Sa pesa cha, ik okcha̱yá,
 Auet is sʋm aiahni na,
 Si achukma̱ka tuk oke.

[V4]
 Chishno atuk keyu hokma,
 Si okcha̱ya he tuk keyu;
 Sʋlla he tuk pulla hoke,
 Ʋba A̱ki Chihowa ma!

[V5]
 Chishno pulla tuk mak ona
 Sai okcha̱ya moma mʋhli,
 Yakoke, ahni biekʋt,
 Chin taloho̱wa li hoke.

[V6]
 Sa chu̱kʋsh, ʋm anukfila,
 Sa shilombish a̱ aiena
 Moma ka pit chihi̱ma lish,
 Chim ʋlla toba la hinla,

[V7]
 Aiahnit, himak nitak a̱
 Chimmi toba sa bʋnna hosh,
 Yakoht chim ilbʋsha lishke,
 Chisʋs ma! Ʋba A̱ki ma!</lyrics>
<aka>Ʋba A̱ki a̱ kana ma, Abeka tuk osh hlakoffi in taloa</aka>
</song>